tags: just leave them alone to enjoy their free time
summary: So once again the guys get bothered during a private family outing... oh sure they look happy and smiley but that’s just bc they...
body:
So once again the guys get bothered during a private family outing… oh sure they look happy and smiley but that’s just bc they are too nice to say.. hey, you know what, we are with family so sorry no photos. 

It drives me nuts that certain ppl in this phandom seem it perfectly acceptable to bother them when they are clearly trying to chill out  and don’t need to be bothered for photos just bc you see them, then apologise for intruding on their family get together.

Why don’t you JUST NOT BOTHER THEM.

The guys rarely see their family as it is and should be left alone to enjoy it, its not fair on them, their family, or friends to bothered by strangers who think the guys are their besties and therefore fine to bother them. Because you aren’t.
